## ğŸ™ï¸ What It Does

SpeakPace lets users upload a **short voice note** (â‰ˆ 60 â€“ 300 seconds) and automatically generates:

* ğŸš **Pace Heatmap** â€” words-per-minute plotted over time
* ğŸ—£ **Filler-Word Report** â€” counts and spikes for â€œumâ€, â€œuhâ€, â€œlikeâ€, etc.
* ğŸ§ **Emphasis Map** â€” visualises pitch and intensity to show where energy drops or peaks
* ğŸ§¾ **Auto-Generated Scripts** â€” 60-second and 5-minute practice scripts with rhythm markers
* ğŸ“‘ **Annotated PDF Report** â€” all analytics and recommendations in a single downloadable file

Itâ€™s designed for **presenters, interviewees, and public-speaking students** who want rapid, data-driven feedback on their speaking pace and delivery.

