## ğŸš€ MVP Focus

The MVP is intentionally **simple and fast**:

* Single-user or coach-led SaaS workflow
* Upload â†’ Analyse â†’ Download
* No admin dashboard or multi-role system
* Works locally (FastAPI backend + React frontend)
* Offline-first mode planned for edge deployments

