## ğŸ›  Frontend Setup (React + Vite + Tailwind v3)

From your root project folder (`/Users/beard/Documents/GitHub/bantering-baboon`):

```bash
# 1. Create the frontend
npm create vite@latest baboon-frontend -- --template react
cd baboon-frontend

# 2. Install dependencies
npm install
npm install -D tailwindcss@3 postcss autoprefixer
npx tailwindcss init -p
npm install react-router-dom

# 3. Configure Tailwind
# In tailwind.config.js:
content: ["./index.html", "./src/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}"],

# 4. Enable Tailwind in src/index.css:
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

# 5. Run the app
npm run dev
```

Test by editing `src/App.jsx`:

```jsx
export default function App() {
  return (
    <div className="flex h-screen items-center justify-center bg-gray-900 text-white">
      <h1 className="text-4xl font-bold">ğŸš€ Bantering Baboon / SpeakPace is live!</h1>
    </div>
  );
}
```

